    Hell Beast exited the CR chamber, his chest was on fire, literally 
burning. Coughing, he rolled ont to his side. He was sick, that was for sure.
    Aquarious walked up to him. "Looks like you need some rest there. Ill 
take you to your quarters." And helped him walk to his room.
    Hell Beast, tired, went to sleep. Meanwhile Aquarious hooked him up to an 
Antivirus computer IV. It was going to sweep through his main data base and 
spark stabilizer.
